Tired of a boring black or white theme wallpaper every time you are browsing on your desktop? Here is how you can switch things up with just a few steps. Step 1 Open Chrome browser. Step 2 In the bottom right, click Customize. In a pen icon. Step 3 Go to Color and theme to choose your desired option. There are a wide range of options but you can also upload from your own gallery. Step 4 Click Done.